<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>My Portfolio</title>
    <style>
        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; background: #0d1117; color: #c9d1d9; line-height: 1.6; }
        header { background: #161b22; padding: 2rem 1rem; text-align: center; border-bottom: 1px solid #30363d; }
        header h1 { color: #58a6ff; font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
        header p { color: #8b949e; font-size: 1.2rem; }
        .container { max-width: 800px; margin: 2rem auto; padding: 0 1rem; }
        h2 { color: #58a6ff; border-bottom: 1px solid #30363d; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .project-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
        @media (max-width: 600px) { .project-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
        .project-card { background: #161b22; border: 1px solid #30363d; border-radius: 6px; padding: 1.5rem; }
        .project-card h3 { color: #f0f6fc; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
        .project-card a { color: #58a6ff; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.9rem; }
        .project-card a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
        .contact-links { display: flex; gap: 1rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
        .contact-links a { color: #58a6ff; text-decoration: none; }
        .contact-links a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Hi, I'm [Your Name]</h1>
        <p>[Your Profession / Role, e.g., Web Developer & Designer]</p>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <section id="about">
            <h2>About Me</h2>
            <p>Write a brief, compelling introduction about your skills, background, and passion here. Keep it to 2-3 sentences to hold the reader's attention.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="projects">
            <h2>Projects</h2>
            <div class="project-grid">
                <div class="project-card">
                    <h3>Project One</h3>
                    <p>A short description of what this project does and the technologies used to build it.</p>
                    <a href="#" target="_blank">View Project &rarr;</a>
                </div>
                <div class="project-card">
                    <h3>Project Two</h3>
                    <p>A short description of what this project does and the technologies used to build it.</p>
                    <a href="#" target="_blank">View Project &rarr;</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="contact">
            <h2>Contact</h2>
            <p>Feel free to reach out for collaborations or opportunities!</p>
            <div class="contact-links">
                <a href="mailto:your.email@example.com">Email Me</a>
                <a href="https://linkedin.com" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>
                <a href="https://github.com" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
